metadata.name: Copy-Cat #1
metadata.description: Copy-Cat #1/128 | Copy-Cats learn from the best; they don't reinvent the wheel - they use it. Copy-Cats value curiosity over knowledge, participation over status. Copy-Cats is the starting point for greatness. Copy-Cats is just the beginning. And when you think you have found the Copy-Cats - the truth is: they have found you.
